player.manager

Class PlayerManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • player.manager.PlayerManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DialogueManager, LevelManager, NodeManager, UpdateView

    public class PlayerManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements DialogueManager, LevelManager, UpdateView
    --------Controller use----------- UpdateView is for Engine to use to update the view in player side --------Player use-------------- DialogueManager is the interface which let dialogScene tell controller to update dialog LevelManager is the interface for GameLevelScene. It has some method to let controller know what operation is made by player.

    Fangyi Chen
